SELECT
  id,
  argMax(name, time),
  groupArrayInsertAt(
    NaN,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(avg, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS avg,
  groupArrayInsertAt(
    [],
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(resolution_levels,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS levels,
  groupArrayInsertAt(
    NaN,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(quantile_0, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS quantile_0,groupArrayInsertAt(
    NaN,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(quantile_1, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS quantile_1,groupArrayInsertAt(
    NaN,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(quantile_2, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS quantile_2,groupArrayInsertAt(
    NaN,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(quantile_3, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS quantile_3,groupArrayInsertAt(
    NaN,
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toDate('2015-1-1'), toDate('2016-12-1'))) + 1)(ROUND(quantile_4, 2),
    toUInt32(dateDiff('year', toStartOfYear(toDate('2015-1-1')), time))) AS quantile_4
FROM
(
  SELECT
    toStartOfYear(opened_at) AS time,
    repo_id AS id, argMax(repo_name, time) AS name,
    avg(resolution_duration) AS avg,
    quantile(0)(resolution_duration) AS quantile_0,quantile(0.25)(resolution_duration) AS quantile_1,quantile(0.5)(resolution_duration) AS quantile_2,quantile(0.75)(resolution_duration) AS quantile_3,quantile(1)(resolution_duration) AS quantile_4,
    [countIf(resolution_level = 0),countIf(resolution_level = 1),countIf(resolution_level = 2),countIf(resolution_level = 3)] AS resolution_levels
  FROM
  (
    SELECT
      repo_id,
      argMax(repo_name, created_at) AS repo_name,
      org_id,
      argMax(org_login, created_at) AS org_login,
      issue_number,
      argMaxIf(action, created_at, action IN ('opened', 'closed' , 'reopened')) AS last_action,
      argMax(issue_created_at,created_at) AS opened_at,
      maxIf(created_at, action = 'closed') AS closed_at,
      dateDiff('day', opened_at, closed_at) AS resolution_duration,
      multiIf(resolution_duration <= 3, 0,resolution_duration <= 7, 1,resolution_duration <= 15, 2, 3) AS resolution_level
    FROM gh_events
    WHERE type = 'PullRequestEvent' AND pull_merged = 1 AND (org_id IN [1342004])
    GROUP BY repo_id, org_id, issue_number
    HAVING opened_at >= toDate('2015-1-1') AND opened_at < toDate('2017-1-1') AND last_action='closed'
  )
  GROUP BY id, time
  
)
GROUP BY id
ORDER BY avg[-1] DESC
    LIMIT 3
